    "Graphvite (Zhu et al. 2019) is a powerful graph embedding engine designed for high-speed and large-scale embedding learning.",
    "It provides a complete training and evaluation process, supports node embedding, knowledge graph embedding, and high-dimensional graph data visualization, and provides a powerful tool for the practical application of graph neural networks.",
    "In general, these graph computing frameworks provide strong support for research and applications of graph neural networks, greatly promoting the field of graph neural networks.",
    "By taking advantage of their strengths, researchers, and developers can process and analyze graph data more efficiently, thus promoting the application and progress of graph neural networks in various fields.",
    "The graph pooling methods have a promising application in bioinformatics, cheminformatics, social networks, natural language processing, computer vision, etc."
